INSERT INTO `feedbacks` VALUES (5,'Rajvender Singh','CEO & Founder Astha Travels','Extremely WoW Trip - Vivan Travels made my Foreign Customer Trip to Very Amaze & Memorable Trip !!! Thanks to Mr Umesh Taglani who helped me to make this Journey a Fantastic Trip to my Customer.','2025-05-13 19:05:41','2025-05-13 19:05:41'),(6,'Mousami Pathak','Travel Vissta','This was my first work with via Vivan Travels. Sikkim and Darjeeling trip was handled by Awesome tours. Mr Umesh Taglani ji & Sanju Singh ji was very co-operative and was very concerned about the travellers and took very good care by calling and enquiring about the tour every day in the evening.It was a overall fantastic trip and Nathula pass was at its best.My Customer had Best Experience and it was best month to have the best mountain views.Stay and travel every thing was good.I would like to thank awesome Vivan Travels and Team.\nRegards,\nMousami Pathak','2025-05-13 19:13:11','2025-05-13 19:13:11');
